'''韋倫斯症候群'''（Wellens' syndrome），是[[左前降支動脈|左前降支動脈]]（left anterior descending，LAD）狹窄型的{{tsl|en|unstable angina|不穩定性心絞痛}}所特有的心電圖變化<ref name=":0">{{cite journal | last = Tandy | first = TK |author2=Bottomy DP |author3=Lewis JG  | title = Wellens' syndrome | journal = Annals of Emergency Medicine | volume = 33 | issue = 3 | pages = 347–351 |date=March 1999 | pmid = 10036351 | doi = 10.1016/S0196-0644(99)70373-2| url = https://zenodo.org/record/1259945 }}</ref>。該徵象對診斷左前降支狹窄具有高度特異性<ref name=":1">{{Cite book|chapter=Wellens Syndrome|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK482490/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=29494097|first=Brianna|last=Miner|first2=William S.|last2=Grigg|first3=Elise H.|last3=Hart}}</ref>。

== 描述 ==
典型心電圖變化為胸前導極（V2、V3）出現雙極性T波或T波倒置的情形。該徵象最初被分為A、B兩型，但後來認為是同一種症候群在不同時間點的時序性變化。一開始會呈現對稱的雙相型（biphasic）[[T波|T波]]倒置，後來會逐漸在胸前導極形成倒深T波<ref name=":0">{{cite journal | last = Tandy | first = TK |author2=Bottomy DP |author3=Lewis JG  | title = Wellens' syndrome | journal = Annals of Emergency Medicine | volume = 33 | issue = 3 | pages = 347–351 |date=March 1999 | pmid = 10036351 | doi = 10.1016/S0196-0644(99)70373-2| url = https://zenodo.org/record/1259945 }}</ref>。

Rhinehart等人在2002年對該症候群進行下列描述<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Electrocardiographic manifestations of Wellens' syndrome|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12442245/|last=Rhinehardt|first=Joseph|last2=Brady|first2=William J.|date=2002-11|journal=The American Journal of Emergency Medicine|issue=7|doi=10.1053/ajem.2002.34800|volume=20|pages=638–643|issn=0735-6757|pmid=12442245|last3=Perron|first3=Andrew D.|last4=Mattu|first4=Amal}}</ref>：

* V2、V3雙極性T波或倒深T波（可能延伸至V1-6）
* ST段微幅（< 1mm）或沒有升高
* 胸前導極無Q波出現
* R波遞增（R wave progression）正常
*近期有心絞痛病史
*該心電圖變化通常發生於無痛期（pain-free state）
*心臟酵素正常或微幅上升
== 臨床意義 ==
該徵象在診斷及預後評估上具有重要的價值。有研究發現，該症候群所有患者的左前降支動脈皆阻塞面積超過50%，平均阻塞面積則高達85%<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Anatomic and prognostic significance of new T-wave inversion in unstable angina|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/6602539/|last=Haines|first=D. E.|last2=Raabe|first2=D. S.|date=1983-07|journal=The American Journal of Cardiology|issue=1|doi=10.1016/0002-9149(83)90061-9|volume=52|pages=14–18|issn=0002-9149|pmid=6602539|last3=Gundel|first3=W. D.|last4=Wackers|first4=F. J.}}</ref>。在診斷[[左前降支動脈|左前降支動脈]]（LAD）狹窄的敏感度為24.6%，特異度為96.2%，具有高度[[特异度|特異性]]，意即發生此徵象者有極高的機會具有左前降支狹窄的問題<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Prevalence and Clinical Implication of Wellens’ Sign in Patients With Non-ST-Segment Elevation Myocardial Infarction|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6575113/|last=Kobayashi|first=Akihiro|last2=Misumida|first2=Naoki|date=2019-6|journal=Cardiology Research|issue=3|doi=10.14740/cr856|volume=10|pages=135–141|issn=1923-2829|pmc=6575113|pmid=31236175|last3=Aoi|first3=Shunsuke|last4=Kanei|first4=Yumiko}}</ref>。

有病例報告顯示{{tsl|en|Takotsubo cardiomyopathy|壓力性心肌症|}}（Takotsubo cardiomyopathy）也會有此變化<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Takotsubo Cardiomyopathy Presenting as Wellens’ Syndrome|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5965163/|last=Taylor|first=R. Scott|last2=Skjerli|first2=Leif|date=2017-05-24|journal=Clinical Practice and Cases in Emergency Medicine|issue=3|doi=10.5811/cpcem.2017.1.32297|volume=1|pages=175–178|issn=2474-252X|pmc=5965163|pmid=29849266|last3=Ashurst|first3=John}}</ref>。

== 治療 ==
若缺乏治療，患者的病程極可能會進展至[[心肌梗塞|心肌梗塞]]。因此除抗血栓藥物治療之外，若無禁忌症，建議進行[[经皮冠状动脉介入治疗|經皮冠狀動脈介入治療]]（PCI）進行根本治療<ref name=":1" />。

== 流行病學 ==
韋倫斯症候群並非罕見狀況，約有14%-18%的不穩定性心絞痛入院的患者會如此表現<ref>{{cite journal | last = de Zwaan | first = C |author2=Bär FW |author3=Janssen JH | title = Angiographic and clinical characteristics of patients with unstable angina showing an ECG pattern indicating critical narrowing of the proximal LAD coronary artery | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-heart-journal_1989-03_117_3/page/657 | journal = American Heart Journal | volume = 117 | issue = 3 | pages = 657–665 |date=March 1989 | pmid = 2784024 | doi = 10.1016/0002-8703(89)90742-4|display-authors=etal}}</ref>，且約8.8%患者具有[[NSTEMI|非ST上升型心肌梗塞]]（NSTEMI）的情形。若在初次發病後，持續監測心電圖24小時，則高達六成的患者在某段時間會有此表現。

== 發現 ==
1979年，葛森（Gerson）等人描述了一群近端LAD狹窄的患者，在進行活動時，胸前導極的心電圖出現了「U波」，當時所指的「U波」是指雙相性T波後半段倒置的部分<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Exercise-induced U-wave inversion as a marker of stenosis of the left anterior descending coronary artery|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/487534/|last=Gerson|first=M. C.|last2=Phillips|first2=J. F.|date=1979-11|journal=Circulation|issue=5|doi=10.1161/01.cir.60.5.1014|volume=60|pages=1014–1020|issn=0009-7322|pmid=487534|last3=Morris|first3=S. N.|last4=McHenry|first4=P. L.}}</ref>。1982年，{{tsl|en|Hein Wellens|亨里克·瓊·喬斯特·韋倫斯}}（Hein J. J. Wellens）等人根據一群不穩定性[[心絞痛|心絞痛]]患者描述了此徵象<ref>{{cite journal | last = de Zwaan | first = C |author2=Bär FW |author3=Wellens HJJ  | title = Characteristic electrocardiographic pattern indicating a critical stenosis high in left anterior descending coronary artery in patients admitted because of impending myocardial infarction | journal = American Heart Journal | volume = 103 | issue = 4 | pages = 730–736 |date=April 1982 | pmid = 6121481 | doi = 10.1016/0002-8703(82)90480-X}}</ref>。

